    Implement waitlist management feature
    
    Adds FIFO queue system for unavailable time slots with features:
    - Join waitlist when time slot unavailable
    - Position tracking (queue number)
    - Notification system when slot becomes available (2-hour window)
    - Admin priority override capability
    - Automatic queue advancement on expiration
    
    API endpoints:
    - POST /api/waitlist
    - GET /api/waitlist/my-queue
    - DELETE /api/waitlist/:id
    
    Includes email notification trigger and waitlist UI components.

